Calculator Using JavaScript and DOM
ğŸ“Œ Project Overview

This project is a basic web-based calculator built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. It performs standard arithmetic operations such as addition, subtraction, multiplication, and division. The calculator uses DOM (Document Object Model) to handle user input and dynamically update the display without refreshing the page.

